 *   - CLIENT_ID       OAuth 2.0 client ID  (Google Cloud Console)
 *   - CLIENT_SECRET   OAuth 2.0 client secret
 *   - REFRESH_TOKEN   OAuth refresh token (generated once via OAuth Playground)
 *   - BUDGET_SHEET_ID ID of the Google Sheet holding budget/occupancy data
 *   - REPORT_EMAIL    Address that receives the weekly email report
 *   - ACCESS_DOMAINS  Email domains allowed to open the dashboard
 *   - ACCESS_CODE     Fallback access code for users outside those domains
 *   - ANTHROPIC_API_KEY  NOT stored here. Add it in the Settings page; it
 *                        is saved to Script Properties, never to source.
